  <brief_title>Study Comparing Amrubicin Versus Topotecan in Patients With Small Cell Lung Cancer Who Have Responded to Prior Therapy.</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase 2 Trial Comparing Amrubicin Versus Topotecan as Second-Line Treatment in Patients With Extensive Small Cell Lung Cancer Sensitive to First-Line Chemotherapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
