  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate the objective tumor response rate of amrubicin or
      standard topotecan therapy when administered as second-line therapy to ED-SCLC patients who
      have chemotherapy sensitive recurrent or progressive.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
